The APC-targeted antigens of the invention can comprise one or more antigenic moieties, and likewise can comprise one or more targeting moieties. Moreover, these moieties can be linked in several ways. For instance, if “T” represents a targeting moiety, and “Ag” represents an antigenic moiety, the APC-targeted antigens of the present invention may be organized as follows:
Ag-T;
T-Ag;
T1-Ag-T2;
T1-[Ag]n-T2 (wherein [Ag]n represents a multiplicity of antigens.
Examples of the general formulas set forth above include:
Ag-C5a agonist peptide;
IFNγ peptide-Ag;
IFNγ peptide-[Ag]n-C5a agonist peptide.
